"Linux & CI-CD Projects"

Projects to Complete. The projects will only use AWS (Amazon Web Services) and Google Cloud Platform (GCP). I will not be adapting these labs for Microsoft's Azure, 
Oracle Cloud or any other CSP's (Cloud Service Providers).

1. 3 Tier Architecture on AWS Cloud: Scalable and secure infrastructure using Terraform on AWS
2. 3 Tier Architecture on GCP Cloud: Scalable and secure infrastructure using Terraform on GCP
3. GitHub Actions: Automate software deployment with CI/CD (Jenkins) using GitHub Actions
4. GitLab: Automate software deployment with CI/CD (Jenkins) using GitLab.
5. Monitoring: Monitor and Analyse application/infrastructure performance using Grafana, Prometheus, and ELK Stack.
6. Containers: Use Docker to containerize a Node.JS application for easy deployment and scaling.
7. Kubernetes: Create a Kubernetes cluster and secure it.


